message.body: Hello
Hello. How's your day going so far?
I slept in....no work today! How about u?
I'm at work, we had off yesterday tho
Does seem like everyone else is off! No one on the subway this morning
Did you do anything for the holidqys?
Not really, just hung out in the park with my dog mostly. What about you?
Cool I spent a few days at a beach front hotel in AC.. Good times!
Sounds nice! Are you in the Philadelphia area?
Yes...I live in philadelphia. How about you (
Me too. Near the Italian market ... Have you lived here long?
Oh nice! I like thqt part of south philly...I'm n germantown..and I'm from philly originally.. Where are u from? What brought u to philly?
I'm from nj, north/central. My sister lived here and my boyfriend at the time found a job here
Oh okay cool
I like philly...but I think I'd like to experience another city..
Interesting choice of name by the way... Cashew
Yeah me too. I've never really lived anywhere else besides where I grew up and here
I've been thinking about Boston, but I think it's kinda expensive
Haha ... I do love cashews
Lol are u q foody?
Hmm. ... I dunno, maybe but I don't eat meat and I feel like meat is a big part of foody culture
I hear that.. I keep it to chicken and fish myself..but I do appreciate the way fish and chicken are prepares by a range of cultures...lol U vegeterian?
For the most part, I'll eat fish once in a while
I hadn't for years, but recently I had some traveling and then I started to crave it sometimes
Nice!
Any good take out recommendations?
Ohh okay gotcha....where did u travel?if ur n s philly I kno u've tried govindas! By broad and south I think
Iceland, Norway, Finland ... They love some seafood!
Govindas is sooo good! I haven't had it in a long time though for some reason
Nice!
I haven't been to most of the world, but I think I can still safely say Norway is the best!
Hey I'm heading Into thr movies...talk to u shortly
K. Have fun!
